re PR bootstrap/43121 (Bootstrap failure)

	PR bootstrap/43121
	* except.c (sjlj_emit_function_enter): Don't call
	add_reg_br_prob_note, instead add REG_BR_PROB note to the last insn
	directly.
	* rtl.h (add_reg_br_prob_note): Remove prototype.
